---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Rawan Aladdin - About Me">
  <div id="overlay" class="overlay"></div>
  <header>
    <div>
      <a href="/index.html" class="back-arrow">&#10229;</a>
      <p class="heading-page">About Me</p>
    </div>
    <div class="full-page-menu">
      <ul class="menu-links">
        <li><a href="/index.html">Home&#8599;</a></li>
        <li><a href="/projects.html">Works&#8599;</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about.html">About&#8599;</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    <article class="about-blurb">
      <div class="audio-container">
        <audio
          controls
          anonymous
          id="about-audio"
          preload="auto"
          src="/about-audio-music.mp3"
          type="sound/mp3"
          onclick="playandLoopThroughText();"
        ></audio>
        <p>Listen to me narrate (and pronounce my name!)</p>
      </div>
      <p class="main-text">
        <span id="blurb" data-nav="blurb1">I'm <strong class="emphasis">Rawan Aladdin</strong></span>
        <span> (yes, like the movie),</span>
        <span>a vibrant designer</span>
        <span> who's an avid history fanatic, </span>
        <span>classic movie-lover,</span>
        <span><strong class="popup-text" id="pic-emoji">amateur photographer&#8599;</strong></span>
        <span>and a <strong class="popup-text" id="cat-emoji">big animal lover&#8599;.</strong></span>
      </p>
      <p class="main-text">
        <span>From the bustling corridors of the University of Toronto</span>
        <span>to the innovative labs at the British Columbia Institute of Technology, </span>
        <span>I've journeyed through the landscapes of Cognitive Science,</span>
        <span>Philosophy, </span>
        <span>Digital Humanities,</span>
        <span>and UX/UI Design. </span>
        <span>Armed with Figma, </span>
        <span>HTML, </span>
        <span>CSS, </span>
        <span>and a knack for Human-Computer Interaction, </span>
        <span>I craft experiences that delight and inspire. </span>
      </p>
      <p class="main-text">
        <span>When I'm not tinkering with prototypes </span>
        <span>or fine-tuning pixels, </span>
        <span>you'll find me diving into the latest trends in Artificial Intelligence, </span>
        <span>Augmented Reality, </span>
        <span>and UX methodologies. </span>
        <span>My adventures have taken me from </span>
        <span>redesigning web layouts for cultural associations </span>
        <span>to leading digital media teams, </span>
        <span>always with a camera in hand </span>
        <span>and a vision in mind.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="main-text">
        <span>Let's create something amazing together! </span>
        <span><a href="/projects.html" class="small-link"><strong id="popup-link">Explore my work&#8599;</strong></a>, </span>
        <span>get inspired, </span>
        <span>and join me on this exciting journey </span>
        <span>of discovery and innovation.</span>
      </p>
    </article>
    <img src="/personalitypic1edited-mask.png" class="rotated-image" />
  </main>

  <script type="text/javascript" defer src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" defer src="/js/components/menu.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" defer src="/js/components/about-image.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" defer src="/js/components/popup-image.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" defer src="/js/components/gsap-fade.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" defer src="/js/index.js"></script>
</BaseLayout>
